OL,3,CCalls for vets to publish price lists
OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,FVets in Jersey are being asked to
OL,7,Fconsider whether they can be more
OL,8,Ftransparent with customers following
OL,9,Fan investigation by the UK's
OL,10,Fcompetition watchdog.
OL,12,FIt concluded that pet owners are not
OL,13,Falways given the full picture of the
OL,14,Fcosts for services and wants a law
OL,15,Frequiring vets there to publish price
OL,16,Flists, provide itemised bills and
OL,17,Fwritten estimates for more costly
OL,18,Ftreatments.
