OL,3,CCalls for vets to publish price lists
OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,FThe UK regulator also calls for vets
OL,7,Fto inform customers about cheaper
OL,8,Foptions that may be on offer, such as
OL,9,Fonline prescriptions, and to disclose
OL,10,Fwho owns a practice to avoid possible
OL,11,Fconflicts of interest.
OL,13,FThe Jersey Competition Regulatory
OL,14,FAuthority says it is not suggesting
OL,15,Fthe island has similar issues and
OL,16,Frecognises vets do publish price lists
OL,17,Ffor certain services.
