OL,3,CCalls for vets to publish price lists
OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,FHowever, in an open letter, it is
OL,7,Fasking vets to consider whether they
OL,8,Fcan help Jersey customers "make better
OL,9,Finformed decisions, compare prices,
OL,10,Fand feel more confident about the
OL,11,Fchoices they are making for their
OL,12,Fpets' care".
OL,14,FSarah Price from the watchdog
OL,15,Fexplains: "This is all about providing
OL,16,Ftransparency for pet owners and they
OL,17,Fcan see it up front.
