OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,F"When you visit the vets, you can
OL,7,Fsometimes be quite vulnerable and it's
OL,8,Fmaking sure you build that trusted
OL,9,Frelationship with them."
OL,11,FJersey cat owner Athena Kallias says
OL,12,Fshe faced an unexpectedly high vet
OL,13,Fbill after an initially incorrect
OL,14,Fdiagnosis led to more tests before
OL,15,Fthey eventually got to the bottom of
OL,16,Fthe issue.
