OL,3,CCalls for vets to publish price lists
OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,FShe explains: "I had the shock of my
OL,7,Flife when I went to pay what I thought
OL,8,Fwas a standard vet visit and there was
OL,9,Fanother #500 charge on there. It just
OL,10,Ffloored me."
OL,12,FJersey vet Roisin Wood says "open and
OL,13,Fhonest conversations" between
OL,14,Fpractices and customers are key, but
OL,15,Fthinks advertising the price of every
OL,16,Ftreatment could do more harm than good.
