OL,3,CCalls for vets to publish price lists
OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,FShe adds: "Just publishing a list of
OL,7,Froutine prices runs the risk of a race
OL,8,Fto the bottom in terms of trying to
OL,9,Fcompete with each other about who can
OL,10,Fprovide services for the least money.
OL,12,F"Whereas actually, when looking to
OL,13,Fchoose a veterinary practice to look
OL,14,Fafter your animals, it's not all about
OL,15,Fprice and who can do a vaccine the
OL,16,Fcheapest.
