OL,3,CCalls for vets to publish price lists
OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,F"Nobody likes talking about money but
OL,7,FI think where there have been issues
OL,8,Fin the UK with pricing, often it's
OL,9,Fdown to poor communication rather than
OL,10,Fpeople perceiving that they're being
OL,11,Fovercharged for services.
OL,13,F"We have been affected as businesses
OL,14,Fby the recent price hikes of goods and
OL,15,Fservices, just like everybody has, and
OL,16,Fthat has to be reflected in what
OL,17,Fyou're charging clients."
