OL,3,CCalls for vets to publish price lists
OL,4,Cto avoid shock bills
OL,6,FAnne-Marie Le Marquand runs a Jersey
OL,7,Fpet shop and supports the publishing
OL,8,Fof a price list so prospective pet
OL,9,Fowners, as well as those who already
OL,10,Fhave animals, can take costs into
OL,11,Faccount.
OL,13,FShe explains: "Quite often we get
OL,14,Fpeople asking us how much it is to go
OL,15,Fto the vets for a check-up, neutering
OL,16,Ftheir rabbits, a lot of people want to
OL,17,Fknow.
OL,19,F"It would be good for them to
OL,20,Fadvertise their prices so that we can
OL,21,Fthen pass them on."
